              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Scattering cross section per hydrogen atom for benzene"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Scattering CS was derived from measured total CS for",
                "benzene molecules by subtraction of absorption CS of",
                "hydrogen and total CS of carbon, each multiplied by",
                "corresponding number of atoms in the molecule, and",
                "subsequent division by number of hydrogen atoms.",
                "Total CS for carbon and absorption CS for hydrogen from",
                "D.J.Hughes,R.B.Schwartz,Atlas of Neutron Cross Sections",
                " (russian translation), Atomizdat,Moscow,1959."
              ]
            }
          ],
